                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A gauntling's fangs carry with them a potent curse that eagerly seeps into living flesh. The first time in a round that a creature takes damage from a gauntling's jaws Strike, they must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:18|options:inflicts:sickened] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} and can't reduce its sickened value below 1 for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but for 1 hour. A creature that dies while under this curse's effects rises within 24 hours as a zombie.</p>"
                },
